# Installation
> `npm install --save @types/n3`

# Summary
This package contains type definitions for N3 (https://github.com/rdfjs/n3.js).

# Details
Files were exported from https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/tree/master/types/n3.
